Name: TC07: Successful account deletion.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully delete their account by accessing the account settings and following the deletion process.

Name: TC27: Unsuccessful creation of a new Project due to invalid information.
Description: This test verifies that the system prevents the creation of a new project when invalid information is provided.

Name: TC22: Unsuccessful task creation with invalid information.
Description: This test verifies that a user cannot create a task with invalid information (when the task name is missing).

Name: TC21: Successful task duplication.
Description:
This test verifies that a user can successfully duplicate a task.
    It ensures that the duplicated task has the same details as the original task and appears in the task list.

Name: TC14: Successful addition of a sub-task.
Description: This test verifies that a sub-task can be successfully added to an existing task.

Name: TC03: Successful logout from an account.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully logout from an account and is redirected to the login page.

Name: TC12: Successful task creation.
Description: This test verifies that a task can be successfully created with all required fields filled.

Name: TC37: Successful search for a task with a specific comment.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully search for a task with a specific comment, ensuring that tasks containing the specified comment are correctly identified and displayed in the search results.

Name: TC20: Successful addition of a label to a task.
Description:
This test verifies that a user can successfully add a label to a task.
    It ensures that the label is visible in the task's details and can be used to filter tasks.

Name: TC30: Successful task moving on Board.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully move a task from one column to another on the Board, ensuring the task's position is updated correctly and persists after a page refresh.

Name: TC28: Successful duplication of a Task List.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully duplicate an existing task list, creating an identical copy.

Name: TC25: Successful change of the Project name and type.
Description: This test verifies that the project name and type can be successfully changed.

Name: TC09: Unsuccessful login to an existing account with invalid information.
Description: This test verifies that a user cannot login to an existing account using invalid credentials, such as incorrect email or password.

Name: TC08: Unsuccessful registration of a new account with invalid information.
Description: This test verifies that a new user cannot register an account when providing invalid information, such as incorrect email format, missing password, or other invalid inputs.

Name: TC34: Successful filtering for a task by its label.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully filter tasks by their label, ensuring the filtered tasks match the specified label and display correctly in the task list.

Name: TC10: Inability to change the current password with an incorrect password.
Description: This test verifies that a user cannot change the current password when providing an incorrect current password.

Name: TC18: Successful task creation with a link.
Description: This test verifies that a task can be successfully created with a link, and clicking the link opens a new browser tab with the correct URL.

Name: TC17: Successful task deletion.
Description: This test verifies that a task can be successfully deleted and is no longer visible in the task list.

Name: TC35: Successful filtering for a task by its due date.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully filter tasks by their due date, ensuring the filtered tasks match the specified date and display correctly in the task list.

Name: TC19: Successful addition of a comment to a task.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully add a comment to a task and that the comment appears in the "Comments" section.

Name: TC33: Successful filtering for a task by its priority.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully filter tasks by their priority, ensuring the filtered tasks match the specified priority and display correctly in the task list.

Name: TC11: Inability to delete the account with an incorrect email or password.
Description: This test verifies that a user cannot delete their account when providing an incorrect email or password.

Name: TC06: Successful email and username change.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully change their email address and username through the account settings.

Name: TC13: Successful change of name, description, and priority for a task.
Description: This test verifies that the name, description, and priority of a task can be successfully updated.

Name: TC23: Successful creation of a new Task List.
Description: This test verifies that a new Task List can be successfully created with a valid name.

Name: TC04: Ability to login using a Google account.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully login using a Google account, including the authorization process via Google's login page.

Name: TC29: Successful archiving of a Project.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully archive a project, confirm its archival in the archived projects section, and restore it back to the active projects section.

Name: TC24: Successful creation of a new Task Board with sections.
Description: This test verifies that a new Task Board can be successfully created with multiple sections.

Name: TC32: Successful search for a task by its description.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully search for a task by its description, ensuring that the correct task is displayed in the search results.

Name: TC16: Successful task completion and marking as completed.
Description: This test verifies that a task can be successfully marked as completed and moved to the "Completed" section.

Name: TC02: Successful login to an existing account with valid information.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully login to an existing account using valid email and password credentials.

Name: TC01: Successful registration of a new account with valid information.
Description: This test verifies that a new account can be successfully registered using valid email, password, and username information.

Name: TC26: Successful deletion of a Project.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully delete an existing project.

Name: TC05: Successful password change.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully change their password through the account settings by entering the current password and a new one.

Name: TC36: Successful search for a task that contains links.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully search for a task containing links, ensuring that tasks with URLs are correctly identified and displayed in the search results.

Name: TC15: Successful change of task due date and time.
Description: This test verifies that the due date and time of an existing task can be successfully updated.

Name: TC31: Successful search for a task by its name.
Description: This test verifies that a user can successfully search for a task by its exact name, ensuring that the correct task is displayed in the search results.
